        "subject": "LU-0000 mdt: [PROTO] remove extra check in rename path",
        "message": "LU-0000 mdt: [PROTO] remove extra check in rename path\n\nthere is no need in the second call to mdt_rename_sanity() in\nrename path - the global rename lock ensures that the result\nof the 1st call is preserved valid.\n\nthe patch should fix deadlock reported in LU-4725.\n\nChange-Id: I13b5a0bcac3cfe014b21288b3675994d7c60ed62\nSigned-off-by: Alex Zhuravlev <alexey.zhuravlev@intel.com>\n"
      },
